The paper deals with image inpainting using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a new approach using adversarial learning, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with edge detection and generation, which falls under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. Finally, the paper evaluates its approach on publicly available datasets, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
